%3D%5C%22openai%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a00b771fb3fcb426487bba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20believe%20I%20would%20say%20this%20one%20day%2C%20but%20I%20am%20burnt%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20former%20OpenAI%20and%20xAI%20staffer%20who's%20returning%20to%20his%20home%20country%20of%20Vietnam.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Thomas%20IllustrationFuller%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20OpenAI%20and%20xAI%20staffer%20says%20he's%20quitting%20frontier%20AI%20labs%20due%20to%20burnout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHieu%20Pham%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20he%20would%20return%20to%20his%20home%20country%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bheal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20believe%20I%20would%20say%20this%20one%20day%2C%20but%20I%20am%20burnt%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Pham%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20helped%20build%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20AI%20systems.%20Now%2C%20he's%20unplugging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20OpenAI%20and%20xAI%20staffer%20says%20the%20breakneck%20pace%20inside%20frontier%20AI%20labs%20left%20him%20burned%20out%2C%20and%20he's%20heading%20home%20to%20Vietnam%20to%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHieu%20Pham%20announced%20his%20departure%20from%20OpenAI%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday%2C%20describing%20his%20time%20at%20OpenAI%20and%20at%20xAI%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-lifetime%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20these%20companies%2C%20I%20have%20helped%20creating%20extremely%20intelligent%20entities%20that%20will%20meaningfully%20improve%20our%20lives.%20The%20work%20makes%20me%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20work%20came%20at%20a%20personal%20cost%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20believe%20I%20would%20say%20this%20one%20day%2C%20but%20I%20am%20burnt%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Pham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20mental%20health%20deteriorating%20that%20I%20used%20to%20scoff%20at%20is%20real%2C%20miserable%2C%20scary%2C%20and%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPham%20started%20at%20xAI%20in%20August%202024%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20OpenAI%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20Before%20his%20announcement%20on%20Thursday%2C%20he%20had%20worked%20at%20OpenAI%20for%20about%207%20months%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPham%20said%20he%20will%20return%20to%20his%20home%20country%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20he%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Btry%20something%20new%2C%20and%20also%20search%20for%20a%20cure%20for%20my%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20I%20will%20heal.%20Until%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239d0d1da-763f-4540-8fdf-c9dab1070170%5C%22%3EWave%20of%20resignations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPham's%20exit%20comes%20as%20a%20string%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutives-board-members-and-researchers-who-left-openai-in-2025-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20researchers%20%3C%2Fa%3Estep%20away%20from%20frontier%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mrinank%20Sharma%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Safeguards%20Research%20Team%20at%20Anthropic%2C%20announced%20his%20departure%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20appear%20to%20be%20approaching%20a%20threshold%20where%20our%20wisdom%20must%20grow%20in%20equal%20measure%20to%20our%20capacity%20to%20affect%20the%20world%2C%20lest%20we%20face%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20my%20time%20here%2C%20I've%20repeatedly%20seen%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20truly%20let%20our%20values%20govern%20our%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresignation-letters-quit-openai-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Jacob%20Silverman%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20there's%20a%20pattern%20of%20top%20researchers%20walking%20away%20and%20publicly%20wrestling%20with%20their%20unease%20about%20the%20technology%20they%20helped%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-safety-researcher-head-of-preparedness-dylan-scand-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDylan%20Scandinaro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20left%20Anthropic%20earlier%20this%20month%20to%20join%20OpenAI%20as%20head%20of%20preparedness%2C%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20advancing%20rapidly.%20The%20potential%20benefits%20are%20great%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20are%20the%20risks%20of%20extreme%20and%20even%20irrecoverable%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20AI%20researchers%20also%20say%20the%20industry%20is%20starting%20to%20resemble%20China's%20infamous%20%26quot%3B996%26quot%3B%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20shorthand%20for%20working%209%20a.m.%20to%209%20p.m.%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-work-culture-silicon-valley-burnout-ai-researchers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esix%20days%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENathan%20Lambert%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20scientist%20at%20the%20Allen%20Institute%20for%20AI%2C%20said%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BLex%20Fridman%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20published%20this%20month%20that%20kind%20of%20intensity%20has%20become%20the%20norm%20at%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20are%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Lambert%20said%2C%20describing%20a%20high-pressure%20culture%20where%20long%20hours%20are%20often%20self-imposed.%20Many%20employees%2C%20especially%20programmers%2C%20buy%20in%20because%20they%20want%20to