ne-tha-god-profile-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECharlamagne%20Tha%20God%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20he%20could%20remember%20wanting%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20restaurant%20chain%20CEO.%20On%20YouTube%2C%20where%20the%20video%20racked%20up%201%20million%20views%2C%20one%20commenter%20summed%20up%20the%20response%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20planning%20on%20going%20to%20Red%20Lobster%20because%20of%20this%20interview%3F%20I%20AM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20industry%20where%20most%20executives%20operate%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20Adamolekun%20has%20turned%20his%20own%20ambition%20into%20a%20proxy%20for%20the%20brand's.%20The%20bet%20is%20that%20if%20diners%20believe%20in%20him%2C%20they'll%20believe%20in%20Red%20Lobster%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Damola%20is%20a%20rock%20star%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Kelly%20O'Keefe%2C%20founding%20partner%20of%20the%20marketing%20consultancy%20Brand%20Federation.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20authentic%20and%20passionate%20in%20what%20he%20believes%20is%20possible%20with%20Red%20Lobster.%20In%20turn%2C%20people%20seem%20to%20believe%20in%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20around%20Adamolekun%20is%20unusual%20in%20the%20restaurant%20business.%20So%2C%20too%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdamola-ademolekun-top-leadership-books-end-year-reading-list-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdamolekun's%20path%20to%20leading%20Red%20Lobster%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He's%20a%20Harvard-trained%20finance%20guy%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20most%20CEOs%20spend%20decades%20rising%20through%20the%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20younger%20CEOs%20around%2C%20he%20casts%20himself%20as%20the%20ultimate%20overachiever.%20Born%20in%20Nigeria%20to%20a%20neurologist%20father%20and%20pharmacist%20mother%2C%20Adamolekun%20was%209%20when%20he%20moved%20with%20his%20family%20to%20the%20United%20States.%20They%20settled%20first%20in%20Illinois%20(where%20he%20tried%20Red%20Lobster)%20and%20then%20Maryland%2C%20where%20he%20attended%20high%20school%20(and%20developed%20a%20taste%20for%20crab).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%26quot%3BBreakfast%20Club%26quot%3B%20interview%2C%20Adamolekun%20said%20his%20parents%20would%20fixate%20on%20that%20single%20B%20on%20his%20report%20card%2C%20never%20mind%20that%20the%20rest%20were%20As.%20%26quot%3B'Whatever%20you%20do%2C%20just%20be%20the%20best%20at%20it.'%20That%20was%20all%20they%20ever%20cared%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Adamolekun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20fine%2C%20since%2C%20as%20Adamolekun%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20very%20little%20evidence%20of%20me%20not%20excelling%20in%20anything%20that%20I've%20tried%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChildhood%20friends%20say%20the%20assessment%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Adamolekun%20they%20remember.%20Xavier%20Martin%2C%20who%20played%20high%20school%20football%20with%20Adamolekun%2C%20remembers%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bfreakishly%26quot%3B%20good%20at%20pretty%20much%20everything.%20A%20rare%20exception%20was%20when%20they%20were%20paired%20together%20in%20driver's%20ed.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20the%20worst%20driver.%20It%20was%20really%20tough%20for%20him%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20he%20wasn't%20the%20best%20at.%20Probably%20the%20only%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun%20went%20on%20to%20Brown%2C%20where%20he%20played%20football%20and%20studied%20economics%20and%20political%20science.%20He%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20After%20getting%20an%20MBA%20from%20Harvard%2C%20Adamolekun%20joined%20the%20hedge%20fund%20run%20by%20billionaire%20John%20Paulson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20Paulson%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20that%20Adamolekun%20pitched%20an%20acquisition%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-pf-changs-meal-deal-chefs-feast-worth-it-review-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EP.F.%20Chang's%2C%20the%20casual%20dining%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20believing%20the%20firm%20could%20accelerate%20the%20brand%20by%20adding%20delivery%20and%20expanding%20internationally.%20When%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20wreaked%20havoc%20on%20the%20industry%2C%20Adamolekun%2C%20then%2031%2C%20installed%20himself%20in%20the%20corner%20office%2C%20becoming%20the%20chain's%20youngest-ever%20and%20first%20Black%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20stepped%20down%20from%20P.F.%20Chang's%20four%20years%20later%2C%20the%20National%20Restaurant%20Association%20estimated%20he%20had%20helped%20bring%20in%20an%20additional%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22P.F.%20Chang's%20CEO%20Damola%20Adamolekin%20with%20employees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62c86a0d114c1e001872c456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeting%20with%20field%20team%20at%20a%20P.F.%20Chang's%20location.%3Cp%3EDamola%20Adamolekun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falden-global-fortress-chatham-all-have-big-stakes-in-media-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFortress%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20meanwhile%20taken%20over%20Red%20Lobster.%20Morgan%20McClure%2C%20its%20managing%20director%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Easked%20Adamolekun%20to%20take%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20inland%20Florida%20in%201968%2C%20Red%20Lobster%20introduced%20generations%20of%20Americans%20to%20lobster%20and%20crab.%20Its%20fortunes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20other%20sit-down%20chains%2C%20began%20to%20shift%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20as%20cheaper%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-fast-food-chains-in-america-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20convenient%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-dream-gig-employees-burrito-blues-fast-food-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20and%20Panera%20Bread%3C%2Fa%3E%20siphoned%20away%20diners.%20The%20concept%20of%20the%20affordable%20sit-down%20restaurant%20where%20a%20family%20could%20gather%20for%20dinner%20on%20a%20Friday%20night%20seemed%20to%20be%20on%20the%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Red%20Lobster%20started%20changing%20hands%20in%202014%2C%20a%20series%20of%20bad%20bets%20followed.%20In%20the%20first%20case%2C%20private%20equity%20firm%20Golden%20Gate%20Capital%20sold%20Red%20Lobster's%20real%20estate%20and%20then%20leased%20it%20back%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20private-equity%20strategy%20that%20left%20the%20chain%20burdened%20with%20fixed%20rent%20payments.%20The%20move%20raised%20short-term%20cash%20but%20became%20a%20significant%20drag%20on%20the%20business%20and%20was%20only%20unwound%20through%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20change%20came%20in%202020%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-owner-never-eating-lobster-ever-again-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThai%20Union%2C%20a%20seafood%20giant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20took%20over%20and%20introduced%20cost-cutting%20measures%20and%20new%20ideas.%20One%20of%20those%20ideas%2C%20hatched%20in%202023%2C%20was%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-endless-shrimp-can-you-eat-at-red-lobster-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eall-you-can-eat%20shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20permanent%20offering.%20Diners%20rose%20to%20the%20challenge%20with%20gusto%2C%20installing%20themselves%20in%20booths%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20requesting%20to-go%20bags%20for%20the%20mountains%20of%20shrimp%20they%20hadn't%20managed%20to%20gulp%20down%20from%20their%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20McClure%20reached%20out%20to%20Adamolekun%20in%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-rise-and-fall-bankruptcy-history-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERed%20Lobster's%20obituary%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20already%20being%20written.%20Adamolekun%2C%20who%20had%20left%20P.F.%20Chang's%2C%20went%20on%20a%20fact-finding%20mission%2C%20visiting%20restaurants%20across%20the%20country%20to%20familiarize%20himself%20with%20menus%20and%20learn%20what%20he%20could%20from%20longtime%20employees%20and%20patrons.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBy%20August%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-red-lobster-saw-why-struggled-what-could-change-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERed%20Lobster%20had%20emerged%20from%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20shuttering%20more%20than%20150%20locations%20during%20its%20restructuring%2C%20and%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20Adamolekun%20would%20be%20steering%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20parted%20at%20the%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20Adamolekun%20says%20of%20his%20relationship%20with%20Fortress.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20gap%2C%20really%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20point%20of%20view%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20the%20best%20way%20to%20turn%20this%20brand%20around%20is.%26quot%3B%20(Bloomberg%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20McClure%20and%20another%20managing%20director%20are%20set%20to%20leave%20Fortress%20and%20the%20Red%20Lobster%20board%2C%20though%20the%20company%20has%20not%20confirmed%20that%20reporting.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-ceo-low-morale-bankruptcy-turnaround-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdamolekun%20replaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20half%20the%20C-suite%20and%20brought%20in%20hospitality%20veterans%20Bob%20Baker%20and%20Larry%20Konecny%20as%20CFO%20and%20COO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20in%20my%20interview%20that%20the%20vibe%20I%20got%20out%20of%20people%20here%20was%20not%20what%20I%20expected.%20I%20would%20have%20expected%20people%20to%20be%20unengaged%2C%20and%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Konecny%20says.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20very%20much%20just%20waiting%20for%20someone%20to%20show%20up%20and%20give%20them%20a%20reason%20to%20believe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20Adamolekun's%20list%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-ceo-sales-boost-launching-new-menu-endless-shrimp-2024-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDamola%2520Adamolekun%252C%2520the%252035%252Dyear%252Dold%2520CEO%2520of%2520Red%2C%2522nail%2520in%2520the%2520coffin%2522%2520for%2520the%2520company.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiving%20the%20menu%20a%20facelift%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20of%20the%20ideas%20came%20directly%20from%20the%20feedback%20Adamolekun%20had%20collected%20during%20his%20listening%20tour.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-ceo-plan-to-revive-the-chain-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHush%20puppies%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20brought%20back.%20Red%20Lobster's%20original%20tartar%20sauce%2C%20which%20previous%20owners%20had%20tinkered%20with%2C%20was%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%20at%20a%20Red%20Lobster%20restaurant%20in%20Alexandria%2C%20VA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e5eb81fb3fcb426486526%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERed%20Lobster's%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%3Cp%3EDeb%20Lindsey%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20they%20rolled%20out%20a%20summery%20Purple%20Haze%20cocktail%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Snoop%20Dogg%20and%20Dr.%20Dre%2C%20and%20launched%20seafood%20boils%2C%20latching%20onto%20a%20viral%20trend%20popularized%20by%20Louisiana%20food%20creators.%20Videos%20of%20delighted%20customers%20cracking%20open%20crab%20legs%20and%20shrimp%20tails%20from%20steaming-hot%20bags%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Sales%20spiked%20overnight%2C%20and%20the%20boils%20became%20a%20permanent%20feature%20of%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun%20is%20also%20working%20to%20improve%20the%20chain's%20value%20proposition.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-2018-review-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEndless%20Shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20off%20the%20menu%2C%20Red%20Lobster%20has%20tried%20out%20a%20%26quot%3BSpendLESS%20Shrimp%26quot%3B%20promotion%20in%20a%20wink%20to%20the%20fiasco.%20For%20around%20%2415.99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20exact%20price%20varies%20by%20market%20%E2%80%94%20you%20get%20a%20plate%20of%20shrimp%20prepared%20three%20different%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20core%20equities%20are%20lobster%2C%20crab%2C%20and%20shrimp%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-ceo-low-morale-bankruptcy-turnaround-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdamolekun%20says%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20what%20we'll%20focus%20on%3A%20the%20things%20people%20love%20to%20come%20to%20Red%20Lobster%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Maze%2C%20editor%20in%20chief%20of%20%3Cem%3ERestaurant%20Business%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20agrees%20the%20decision%20to%20make%20the%20face%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-ceo-plan-to-revive-the-chain-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestaurant%20revival%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20CEO%20was%20unconventional.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20think%2C%20'Let's%20put%20the%20finance%20guy%20in%20the%20ads%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20this%20case%2C%20it%20was%20just%20smart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20attention%20that%20came%20to%20Red%20Lobster%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you%20file%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20in%20some%20respects%2C%20it's%20weirdly%20good%20marketing%2C%26quot%3B%20Maze%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20he%20gave%20people%20something%20to%20be%20excited%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20suggest%20Adamolekun's%20strategy%20is%20paying%20off.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlacer.ai%2C%20which%20tracks%3C%2Fa%3E%20consumer%20habits%2C%20reports%20Red%20Lobster%20began%20seeing%20consistent%20gains%20in%20average%20monthly%20visits%20last%20June%2C%20the%20first%20such%20streak%20since%202023.%20Consumer%20Edge%2C%20a%20consumer%20data-tracking%20firm%2C%20found%20that%20average%20transaction%20sizes%20rose%2010%25%20year%20over%20year%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20advantage%20of%20private%20equity%20ownership%2C%20says%20Rick%20Munarriz%2C%20an%20analyst%20for%20The%20Motley%20Fool%2C%20is%20time.%20Without%20quarterly%20earnings%20pressure%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20urgency%20of%20a%20turnaround%20can%20stretch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20backdrop%20remains%20unforgiving.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-keep-restaurant-industry-afloat-survey-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmericans%20are%20eating%20out%20less%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20and%20labor%20costs%20have%20climbed%3C%2Fa%3E%20roughly%2035%25%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20CEO%20Damola%20Adamolekun%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694bfeae04eda4732f2e15d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdamolekun%20gives%20regular%20interviews%20and%20navigates%20social%20media%20with%20ease.%20His%20interview%20on%20The%20Breakfast%20Club%20podcast%20has%201%20million%20views%20on%20YouTube.%3Cp%3EPaula%20Lobo%2FAmerican%20Broadcasting%20Companies%2C%20Inc.%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMunarriz%20and%20others%20say%20their%20chief%20concern%20is%20whether%20Adamolekun's%20strategy%20is%20bold%20enough.%20%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20eats%20at%20a%20Red%20Lobster%20roughly%20every%20other%20month%2C%20I%20see%20the%20changes.%20I%20don't%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Munarriz%20says.%20He%20says%20he's%20waiting%20to%20see%20more%20on%20operational%20changes%20that%20could%20improve%20efficiency%20and%20profitability%20across%20the%20chain's%20roughly%20500%20remaining%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20less%20like%20a%20reinvention%20than%20a%20cleanup%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mike%20Perry%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20creative%20agency%20Tavern.%20He%20predicts%20the%20strategy%20will%20keep%20the%20chain%20afloat%2C%20for%20now%2C%20but%20adds%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20make%20you%20an%20icon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20tethering%20the%20brand's%20revival%20tightly%20to%20one%20person%20is%20also%20a%20risky%20bet%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20turnarounds%20are%20long%20and%20CEOs%2C%20especially%20those%20backed%20by%20private%20equity%2C%20don't%20tend%20to%20stick%20around.%20P.F.%20Chang's%20has%20already%20cycled%20through%20three%20CEOs%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpf-changs-ceo-damola-adamolekun-red-lobster-bankruptcy-filing-fortress-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdamolekun%20stepped%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20including%20two%20in%202025%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20underscoring%20how%20quickly%20both%20leadership%20and%20narrative%20can%20shift%20after%20a%20private-equity-backed%20turnaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20story%20is%20the%20CEO%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Perry%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20happens%20to%20the%20story%20when%20he%20leaves%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20diners%2C%20the%20shift%20feels%20real.%20Destiny%20Howard%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20content%20creator%2C%20remembers%20Red%20Lobster%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfancy%20place%20to%20go%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20family%20and%20other%20Black%20families%2C%20but%20says%20it%20faded%20from%20her%20life%20as%20she%20got%20older.%20She's%20back%20as%20a%20loyal%20customer%2C%20and%20calls%20her%20support%20for%20Adamolekun's%20efforts%20a%20%26quot%3Bno-brainer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20see%20someone%20that%20looks%20like%20you%20represent%20them%20in%20a%20positive%20light%2C%20that's%20what%20stands%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun%20says%20he's%20playing%20the%20long%20game.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20go%20bankrupt%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20fix%20everything%20that%20caused%20the%20bankruptcy%20overnight%2C%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20the%20company%20is%20successful%20and%20it%20goes%20back%20to%20being%20one%20of%20the%20great%20restaurant%20companies%20in%20America%2C%20I'll%20be%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun%20plans%20to%20revisit%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20worked%20for%20him%20at%20P.F.%20Chang's%2C%20such%20as%20improving%20takeout%2C%20expanding%20into%20consumer%20packaged%20goods%2C%20and%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20loyalty%20program%20to%20drive%20repeat%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20quite%20a%20bit%20that%20we%20did%20that%20I%20think%20will%20translate%2C%20and%20some%20things%20that%20don't%20translate%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%2C%20you%20know%2C%20copy-paste%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20that%20we%20did%20successfully%2C%20that%20we%20can%20do%20here%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iconic%20Red%20Lobster%20sign%20is%20seen%20from%20the%20highway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e50651fb3fcb426486499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223799%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Red%20Lobster%20sign%20in%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Kosienski%2FSipa%20USA%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20overseeing%20the%20rollout%20of%20a%20more%20modern%20look.%20%26quot%3BOur%20restaurants%20are%20old%2C%20right%3F%20We've%20been%20around%20for%2060%20years%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20in%20need%20of%20a%20refresh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun%20says%20they're%20making%20every%20effort%20to%20keep%20consumer%20costs%20low%2C%20even%20while%20inflation%20and%20supply%20chain%20uncertainty%20mean%20many%20operators%20are%20passing%20along%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-pass-higher-food-costs-diners-inflation-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice%20hikes%20to%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20priority%20is%20wedging%20Red%20Lobster%20back%20into%20the%20popular%20imagination%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20marking%20special%20occasions%20like%20birthdays%2C%20anniversaries%2C%20or%20a%20first%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20that%2C%20Adamolekun%20might%20have%20some%20work%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meal%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-first-time-review-surprising-things-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETimes%20Square%20Red%20Lobster%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ganguly%20gave%20a%20positive%20review%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Breally%20enjoyable%2C%26quot%3B%20if%20not%20quite%20%26quot%3Bmind-blowing.%26quot%3B%20They%20liked%20the%20lobster%20tail%20entr%C3%A9e.%20The%20linguine%20was%20good%2C%20too%2C%20though%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ratio%20of%20lobster%20relative%20to%20the%20pasta%20was%20a%20bit%20low.%26quot%3B%20The%20cheddar%20bay%20biscuits%20were%20just%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWouldn't%20say%20it's%20an%20early-date%20restaurant%2C%26quot%3B%20Gransuly%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20people%20in%20a%20comfortable%20long-term%20relationship%2C%20not%20a%20bad%20date%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fkatherine-tangalakis-lippert%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20covering%20the%20food%20and%20restaurant%20industries.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772096821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f73d9e8408f66718047a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Endless%20Shrimp'%20turned%20Red%20Lobster%20into%20a%20punchline.%20Now%20a%20star%20CEO%20is%20leading%20its%20high-stakes%20turnaround%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20UP%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20takes%20spin%20on%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20futuristic%20Maglev%20train%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772096768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128808341%2Cimgsize-1074897.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findi