20means.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20found%20it%20hilarious%20and%20said%20the%20clips%20made%20them%20proud%20to%20be%20Chinese.%20Others%20just%20cringed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Americans%20want%20to%20be%20Chinese%20now.%20China%20isn't%20sure%20how%20to%20feel%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20TikTok%2C%20non-Chinese%20American%20creators%20are%20filming%20themselves%20boiling%20apples%2C%20practicing%20tai%20chi%20at%20sunrise%2C%20and%20drinking%20hot%20water%20%E2%80%94%20all%20soundtracked%20to%20traditional%20Chinese%20instrumentals%20or%20clips%20from%20Mulan.%20They%20call%20it%20%26quot%3BChinamaxxing%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20videos%20are%20pulling%20in%20millions%20of%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20self-care%2C%20part%20aesthetic%20role-play%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinamaxxing-tiktok-chinese-habits-wellness-hot-water-boiled-apples-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E%20taps%20into%20what%20creators%20portray%20as%20a%20calmer%2C%20healthier%20Chinese%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20%26quot%3BChinamaxxing%26quot%3B%20may%20reflect%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20younger%20Americans%20view%20China%2C%20and%20could%20signal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-retail-brands-labubu-luckin-expand-us-open-stores-data-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChinese%20soft%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Chinese%20social%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-app-xiaohongshu-americans-tiktok-ban-help-homework-rednote-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplatform%20RedNote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20users%20have%20been%20watching%20closely.%20Their%20reactions%20range%20from%20amused%20pride%20to%20bewilderment%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20outright%20cringe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20see%20more%20and%20more%20people%2