%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNTzvAnm3PmU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECall%20Her%20Daddy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BLizzie%20McGuire%26quot%3B%20star%20spoke%20about%20navigating%20a%20divorce%20in%20her%20late%2020s%20and%20how%20motherhood%20shaped%20her%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20split%20from%20her%20first%20husband%2C%20Mike%20Comrie%2C%20in%202015.%20They%20share%20a%20son%2C%20Luca%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20from%20my%20parents'%20divorce%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20show%20my%20kid%20that%20you've%20got%20to%20fight%20for%20your%20happiness.%20And%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20better%20to%20do%20it%20when%20he%20was%20younger%20than%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20when%20he%20was%20five%20and%20aware%2C%20or%20eight%20and%20aware%2C%26quot%3B%20Duff%20told%20podcast%20host%20Alex%20Cooper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20added%20that%20kids%20can%20sometimes%20blame%20themselves%20when%20their%20parents'%20marriage%20doesn't%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20if%20Luca%20cannot%20remember%20this%20and%20have%20two%20lives%20that%20exist%20that%20he%20can%20be%20happy%20in%20and%20feel%20secure%20in%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20winning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20said%20therapy%20was%20essential%20in%20helping%20her%20process%20the%20end%20of%20her%20marriage%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20the%20experience%20taught%20her%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20fight%20for%20yourself%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20that%20you%20have%20kids.%20Your%20kids%20are%20going%20to%20be%20OK.%20You%20know%20what%20I%20mean%3F%20You%20just%20have%20to%20show%20them%20that%20you%20also%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Duff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20lose%20yourself%20in%20your%20child%20and%20feel%20like%20their%20needs%20should%20outweigh%20your%20own%2C%20she%20said.%20But%20she%20added%20it%20was%20also%20%26quot%3Bimportant%26quot%3B%20not%20to%20let%20that%20be%20the%20deciding%20factor%20in%20whether%20she%20stayed%20in%20an%20unhappy%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20added%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-triplets-struggles-mom-guilt-financial-costs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emom%20guilt%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20sometimes%20overshadow%20her%20own%20feelings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20part%20of%20your%20brain%20where%20you're%20like%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20I'm%20still%20in%20here%2C%20and%20I'm%20still%20me%2C'%20and%20then%20there's%20this%20huge%20shadow%20over%20it%20that's%20like%2C%20'But%20everything%20for%20the%20family%20and%20everything%20for%20your%20kid%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20added%20that%20finding%20balance%20between%20motherhood%20and%20her%20own%20identity%20is%20something%20she%20has%20to%20work%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20constant%20conversation%20to%20choose%20yourself%20and%20choose%20something%20you%20know%20that%20you%20enjoy%20outside%20of%20family%20life%20and%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Duff%20married%20Matthew%20Koma%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20has%20three%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuff%20isn't%20the%20only%20celebrity%20who%20has%20spoken%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnesting-divorce-helps-coparent-financially-responsible-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enavigating%20divorce%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202022%20podcast%20appearance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkim-kardashian-in-tears-describes-coparenting-with-kanye-west-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKim%20Kardashian%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20she%20tries%20to%20protect%20Ye%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Kanye%20West%2C%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Beyes%20of%20my%20kids%2C%20for%20my%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20day%20my%20kids%20will%20thank%20me%20for%20not%20sitting%20here%20and%20bashing%20their%20dad%20when%20I%20could.%20They'll%20thank%20me%20and%20I'll%20privately%20answer%20anything%20that%20they%20want%20to%20know.%20But%20it's%20not%20my%20place%20anymore%20to%20jump%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiranda-kerr-co-parent-divorce-peacefully-orlando-bloom-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiranda%20Kerr%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20choosing%20forgiveness%20helped%20her%20co-parent%20peacefully%20with%20her%20ex%2C%20Orlando%20Bloom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20a%20child%20with%20someone%20else%2C%20they're%20always%20going%20to%20be%20that%20person's%20parent%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20life.%20There%20are%20going%20to%20be%20situations%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20talk%20if%20you%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20So%20why%20not%20make%20it%20harmonious%3F%26quot%3B%20Kerr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhilary-duff-divorce-helped-model-self-worth-son-happiness-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772083548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699faaee1fb3fcb426487a90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhilary-duff-divorce-helped-model-self-worth-son-happiness-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20constant%20conversation%20to%20choose%20yourself%20and%20choose%20something%20you%20know%20that%20you%20enjoy%20outside%20of%20family%20life%20and%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20Hilary%20Duff%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhilary-duff-divorce-helped-model-self-worth-son-happiness-2026-2%22%