Rubin%20chips%20to%20addressing%20an%20emerging%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CES%202026%2C%20an%20annual%20consumer%20electronics%20trade%20show%2C%20in%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f7ca91fb3fcb426487915%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia's%20strong%20Q4%20earnings%20are%20calming%20investor%20nerves%20amid%20stock%20fatigue%20in%20the%20AI%20sector.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Marcus%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia's%20strong%20Q4%20earnings%20are%20calming%20investor%20nerves%20amid%20stock%20fatigue%20in%20the%20AI%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20discussed%20its%20future%20risks%20and%20its%20deal%20with%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20shipped%20its%20first%20Vera%20Rubin%20chips%2C%20promising%20faster%20performance%20and%20better%20energy%20efficiency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20moved%20quickly%20to%20calm%20investor%20nerves%20during%20its%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chipmaker%20delivered%20another%20blowout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-q4-earnings-live-updates-ai-chips-rubin-jensen-huang-2026-2%23nvidia-just-shipped-its-first-vera-rubin-samples-to-customers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearnings%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20underscored%20how%20little%20momentum%20the%20AI%20boom%20has%20lost.%20As%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20by%20market%20capitalization%2C%20Nvidia%20topped%20Wall%20Street%20expectations%20across%20the%20board%20in%20its%20fiscal%20fourth%20quarter%20and%20issued%20a%20forecast%20that%20sailed%20past%20analyst%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upbeat%20results%20arrive%20at%20a%20delicate%20moment%20for%20AI-linked%20stocks%2C%20which%20have%20recently%20shown%20signs%20of%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20incorporating%20Groq%20into%20Nvidia%20systems%20to%20an%20update%20on%20the%20new%20Vera%20Rubin%20chips%2C%20here%20are%20the%20biggest%20takeaways%20from%20Nvidia's%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225deeb594-11e9-43d7-a2c2-c2c7532fe25d%5C%22%3E1.%20Nvidia%20is%20becoming%20the%20backbone%20of%20Big%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20call%2C%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20repeatedly%20positioned%20Nvidia%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20AI%20industry's%20biggest%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20latest%20Codex%20model%20is%20trained%20and%20runs%20on%20Nvidia's%20Blackwell%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20companies%20are%20close%20to%20reaching%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20partnership%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20deploying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-groq-gpus-ipus-hot-commodity-ai-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20push%20toward%20superintelligence%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20also%20announced%20an%20up%20to%20%2410%20billion%20investment%20in%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20form%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20from%20large%20language%20models%20to%20robotics%20%E2%80%94%20is%20built%20on%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20take%20the%20great%20opportunity%20that%20we%20have%20as%20we're%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20new%20computing%20era%2C%20this%20new%20computing%20platform%20shift%2C%20to%20put%20everybody%20on%20Nvidia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a65c4126-f7dc-4e50-8adc-00516fc85626%5C%22%3E2.%20Huang%20teases%20Groq%20integration%20as%20AI%20shifts%20to%20inference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20Nvidia's%20future%20road%20map%20and%20whether%20it%20plans%20to%20build%20customized%20chips%20for%20specific%20workloads%2C%20Huang%20said%20the%20company%20prefers%20to%20keep%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20within%20a%20single%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20he%20teased%20a%20potentially%20significant%20move%20involving%20Groq%2C%20saying%20more%20details%20would%20come%20at%20Nvidia's%20GTC%20conference%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20year%2C%20Nvidia%20struck%20a%20non-exclusive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-groq-deals-silicon-valley-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elicensing%20agreement%20with%20Groq%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20low-latency%20AI%20inference%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deal%20that%20also%20brought%20Groq's%20founder%20and%20other%20top%20engineers%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we'll%20do%20is%20we'll%20extend%20our%20architecture%20with%20Groq%20as%20an%20accelerator%20in%20very%20much%20the%20ways%20that%20we%20extended%20Nvidia's%20architecture%20with%20Mellanox%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20networking%20company%20Nvidia%20acquired%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20workloads%20shift%20from%20training%20large%20models%20to%20running%20them%2C%20the%20move%20suggests%20Nvidia%20isn't%20going%20to%20abandon%20its%20core%20platform%20but%20rather%20fold%20specialized%20inference%20capabilities%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5820462-f6fb-455b-83d0-49ca750dd752%5C%22%3E3.%20Samples%20of%20the%20Vera%20Rubin%20chips%20have%20been%20shipped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20begun%20shipping%20early%20samples%20of%20its%20next-generation%20Vera%20Rubin%20chips%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20Financial%20Officer%20Colette%20Kress%20said%20during%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20delivered%20%26quot%3Bour%20first%20Vera%20Rubin%20samples%26quot%3B%20earlier%20this%20week%20and%20expects%20broader%20shipments%20of%20the%20new%20chips%20to%20begin%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20every%20cloud%20model%20builder%20to%20deploy%20Vera%20Rubin%2C%26quot%3B%20Kress%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20previou