87%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AMC%20Theatres%20is%20offering%20a%20new%20perk%20to%20its%20loyalty%20program%20members%3A%20Customers%20who%20pay%20a%20monthly%20fee%20for%20A-List%20or%20Stubs%20Premiere%20will%20get%20priority%20access%20to%20the%20best%20seats%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20program%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20in%202026%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20Adam%20Aron%20on%20Tuesday%E2%80%99s%20earnings%20call.%20This%20change%20comes%20three%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rebecca%20Rubin%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20wants%20Big%20Tech%20to%20build%20its%20own%20power%20plants.%20That's%20already%20starting%20to%20happen.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Trump%20at%20a%20podium%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e158450f42603b0f8d405%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20gave%20his%20annual%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20speech%20before%20Congress.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20wants%20data%20centers%20to%20supply%20their%20own%20electricity%20with%20private%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Cleanview%20report%20found%2046%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20US%20plan%20to%20build%20on-site%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20them%20will%20run%20on%20natural%20gas%2C%20though%20tech%20giants%20have%20clean%20energy%20commitments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20data%20center%20boom%20has%20triggered%20a%20dramatic%20spike%20in%20electricity%20costs%2C%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20stop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20Trump%20said%20at%20Tuesday's%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20that%20he%20issued%20a%20mandate%20for%20data%20centers%20to%20build%20their%20own%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he'd%20%26quot%3Bnegotiated%26quot%3B%20a%20ratepayer%20protection%20pledge%20with%20major%20technology%20companies%20and%20billed%20it%20as%20a%20unique%20solution%20to%20Big%20Tech's%20mounting%20power%20demand%20that%20would%20also%20protect%20American%20consumers%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-electricity-consumers-discounts-utilities-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigher%20electricity%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20build%20their%20own%20power%20plants%20as%20part%20of%20their%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20data%20center%20sites%20have%20already%20started%20building%20their%20own%20power%20plants.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20this%20buildout%20will%20initially%20run%20on%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-runs-dirty-power-and-the-public-pays-the-price-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20giants'%20clean%20energy%20commitments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20a%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20gave%20the%20following%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BMajor%20Tech%20companies%20will%20join%20President%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%20next%20week%20to%20formally%20sign%20the%20Rate%20Payer%20Protection%20Pledge%20that%20he%20announced%20during%20his%20historic%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address.%20Under%20this%20bold%20initiative%2C%20these%20massive%20companies%20will%20build%2C%20bring%2C%20or%20buy%20their%20own%20power%20supply%20for%20new%20AI%20data%20centers%2C%20ensuring%20that%20Americans'%20electricity%20bills%20will%20not%20increase%20as%20demand%20grows.%20President%20Trump%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20American%20AI%20dominance%20while%20simultaneously%20lowering%20costs%20for%20working%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Amazon%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20attend%20the%20White%20House%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ratepayer%20Protection%20Pledge%20is%20an%20important%20step.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20Administration's%20work%20to%20ensure%20that%20data%20centers%20don't%20contribute%20to%20higher%20electricity%20prices%20for%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20vice%20chair%20and%20president%20Brad%20Smith%20wrote%20in%20an%20e-mailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Anthropic%20referred%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSarahKHeck%2Fstatus%2F2026493881614057810%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20last%20night%20by%20Sarah%20Heck%2C%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20external%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20families%20shouldn't%20pick%20up%20the%20tab%20for%20AI.%20In%20support%20of%20the%20%40WhiteHouse%20ratepayer%20protection%20pledge%2C%20Anthropic%20has%20committed%20to%20covering%20100%25%20of%20electricity%20price%20increases%20that%20consumers%20face%20from%20data%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20Heck%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20have%20previously%20announced%20commitments%20to%20covering%20the%20costs%20of%20electricity%20consumption%20at%20their%20data%20centers%2C%20though%20details%20on%20those%20plans%20remain%20scant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22753e8c8d-21dd-45bc-8095-958ac7472e2c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Tech%20is%20building%20its%20own%20power%20plants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20year%2C%20on-site%20power%20plants%20fueled%20mostly%20by%20natural%20gas%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20strategy%20for%20data%20center%20developers%20looking%20to%20stay%20ahead%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%20Meanwhile%2C%20US%20power%20demand%20has%20reached%20record%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bills-surge-utilities-31b-rate-increases-2025-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUtilities%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20asked%20state%20regulators%20to%20approve%20%2431%20billion%20in%20rate%20increases%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20amount%20sought%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20research%20from%20PowerLines%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20advocate%20for%20utility%20customers.%20Many%20of%20those%20requests%20occurred%20in%20places%20experiencing%20heavy%20data%20center%20development%2C%20such%20as%20Virginia%2C%20Texas%2C%20Utah%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20framed%20data%20center%20developers%20building%20their%20own%20power%20plants%20as%20part%20of%20his%20broader%20promise%20to%20ensure%20that%20Big%20Tech%20pays%20for%20the%20infrastructure%20needed%20to%20power%20AI%20ambitions.%20For%20developers%2C%20building%20an%20on-site%20power%20plant%20can%20bypass%20long%20wait%20times%20for%20a%20grid%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-data-center-colossus-power-memphis-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20most%20prominent%20example%20of%20this.%20Musk%20has%20drawn%20intense%20scrutiny%20in%20Tennessee%20and%20Mississippi%2C%20where%20he%20has%20deployed%20unpermitted%20mobile%20generators%20to%20quickly%20get%20his%20data%20centers%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20brought%20his%20first%20mobile%20generators%20to%20Memphis%20in%202024.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20dozens%20of%20data%20centers%20%E2%80%94%20about%2030%25%20of%20all%20planned%20data%20center%20capacity%20in%20the%20nation%20%E2%80%94%20plan%20to%20build%20their%20own%20power%20plants%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20issued%20this%20month%20from%20Cleanview%2C%20a%20data%20visualization%20software%20company%20that%20tracks%20clean%20energy%20and%20data%20center%20projects.%20Nearly%20all%20of%20that%20planned%20capacity%20%E2%80%94%2090%25%20%E2%80%94%20was%20added%20in%202025%2C%20Cleanview%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20review%20of%20permit%20documents%2C%20corporate%20filings%2C%20press%20releases%2C%20and%20local%20news%20stories%2C%20Cleanview%20identified%2046%20data%20center%20projects%2C%20many%20of%20them%20already%20under%20construction%2C%20that%20plan%20to%20draw%20power%20%26quot%3Bbehind%20the%20meter%26quot%3B%20by%20building%20on-site%2C%20private%20power%20plants%20that%20don't%20need%20a%20grid%20connection%20or%20service%20from%20the%20local%20utility%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20Meta's%20plans%20to%20build%20an%20on-site%20natural%20gas%20plant%20for%20its%20data%20center%20in%20New%20Albany%2C%20Ohio%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Oracle%20and%20OpenAI's%20plans%20to%20power%20their%20Project%20Jupiter%20data%20center%20site%20in%20New%20Mexico%20with%20two%20massive%20natural%20gas-fired%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20often%20tout%20their%20commitments%20to%20clean%20energy%2C%20Cleanview's%20review%20of%20behind-the-meter%20permit%20documents%20found%20that%20natural%20gas%20powered%2075%25%20of%20all%20equipment%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20have%20said%20they%20want%20to%20power%20AI%20with%20clean%20technology%2C%20such%20as%20small%20modular%20nuclear%20reactors%20and%20geothermal%20energy.%20Much%20of%20it%20is%20still%20years%20away%20from%20being%20deployed%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c08c5bad-aa7b-45a2-a2ee-8f4fc9e63e89%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETexas%20is%20becoming%20the%20top%20state%20for%20new%20data%20centers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECleanview%20found%20that%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20the%20behind-the-meter%20buildout%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-data-centers-virginia-top-market-status-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappening%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20soon%20overtake%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-centers-energy-grid-electricity-virginia-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVirginia%20as%20the%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20capital%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20reported%20on%20Oracle%20and%20OpenAI's%20plan%20to%20power%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-building-natural-gas-microgrid-at-new-texas-data-center-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStargate%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Texas%20with%20on-site%20natural%20gas%20plants%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffermi-america-reit-utility-irs-rules-corporate-structure-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFermi%20America%3C%2Fa%3E's%20pitch%20to%20build%20the%20world's%20largest%20combined%20data%20center%20and%20power%20plant%20in%20the%20state's%20Panhandle%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Texas%2C%20the%20top%20five%20states%20with%20the%20most%20planned%20behind-the-meter%20capacity%20are%20New%20Mexico%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Utah%2C%20and%20Wyoming.%20West%20Virginia%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20Ohio%2C%20Virginia%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20also%20have%20significant%20behind-the-meter%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20for%20this%20reporter%3F%20Contact%20Ellen%20Thomas%20at%20ethomas%40insider.com%20or%20on%20Signal%20at%20929-524-6964.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-on-site-power-plants-trump-announces-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772061321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f6bd650f42603b0f8eb15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-on-site-power-plants-trump-announces-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20urged%20tech%2