F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D493791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20grandmothers%E2%80%99%20gardens%20to%20modern%20balconies%2C%20marigolds%20have%20been%20a%20constant%20in%20Indian%20households.%20Planted%20in%20October%2C%20they%20brighten%20homes%2C%20protect%20crops%2C%20and%20add%20colour%20to%20every%20celebration.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%20behind%20the%20ritual.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493791%2Findian-grandmothers-how-to-grow-marigolds-october-tradition-gardening-steps-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Born%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20Slum%2C%20This%20Inspiring%20Dropout%20Uses%20Football%20To%20Keep%2026000%20Kids%20in%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ashok%20Rathod%20was%2018%2C%20he%20began%20gathering%20children%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20slum%20for%20weekend%20football%20matches.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20had%20no%20great%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20kids%20away%20from%20addiction%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%2C%20which%20had%20consumed%20many%20of%20his%20own%20friends.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20small%20effort%20grew%20into%20the%20OSCAR%20(Organization%20for%20Social%20Change%2C%20Awareness%20and%20Responsibility)%20Foundation%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20that%20today%20has%20touched%20thousands%20of%20young%20lives%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20lives%20is%20that%20of%20Yamini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20rainy%20afternoon%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20shy%20Class%209%20student%20walked%20nervously%20into%20a%20ground%20where%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20gathered%20children.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A