%2F261821%2Finspiring-uttarakhand-teacher-pandemic-village-students-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20is%20as%20much%20about%20care%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20it%20is%20about%20books.%20You%20have%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20spark%20curiosity%2C%20and%20show%20children%20that%20education%20can%20change%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pauses%2C%20then%20adds%20softly%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%20the%20classrooms%20were%20empty%2C%20and%20I%20cried.%20Today%2C%20those%20rooms%20echo%20with%20chatter%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20learning.%20That%20is%20my%20biggest%20reward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757068200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twelve%20years%20ago%2C%20Sangeeta%20Maurya%20cried%20at%20her%20posting%20in%20Raebareli%20when%20only%2030%20of%20130%20students%20turned%20up.%20Today%2C%20through%20stories%2C%20songs%2C%20and%20compassion%2C%20she%20has%20filled%20her%20classrooms%20with%20laughter%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20proving%20that%20teaching%20in%20villages%20is%20more%20than%20a%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496794%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-rural-school-teacher-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-sangeeta-maurya%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20More%20Parents%20Are%20Adding%20Millets%20%26amp%3B%20Microgreens%20to%20Their%20Kids%E2%80%99%20Lunchboxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Sanchita%20Daswani%2F%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fgreen-organic-raw-microgreen-sprouts-ready-2452650587%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%